Antagony smiled and followed. It wasn't too much a problem for her if she 
distracted Perndabot from duty. She was sure that he could accomplish 
anything he might have not done when he got back. She went over in her mind 
what the meeting with Zardus would be like, because her unusual talent made 
it possible to see into the future.
